  displayTitle: Sap Happens
  openingStory: A syrupy trail leads through two enormous blobs of jungle sap. It
    smells like dessert and behaves like glue.
  successStory: Two magnificent pops later, Gassy Gorilla is free, flying, and only
    slightly shinier.
  lessonText: Sap slows you but cannot defeat you. Tap once to pop free without spending
    fuel.
